BUILD:
docker-compose  build --parallel

RUN
docker-compose up

NOTE:

Curl to get transactions:
curl -X GET "https://localhost:5000/Market" -H  "accept: text/plain"

Curl to post transaction:
curl -X POST "https://localhost:5000/Market?personId=6082e7b1-62fc-47d0-87a6-7e63e792e715&currency=1&amount=100" -H  "accept: */*" -d ""
where:
* personId = must be a guid
* currency must be a values 1-3
** 1-usd
** 2-gbp
** 3-eur
* amount, range 1-1000000000